org.apache.jena.rdfconnection

Class RDFConnectionFuseki

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jena.rdfconnection.RDFConnectionRemote
      • org.apache.jena.rdfconnection.RDFConnectionFuseki
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable, RDFConnection, RDFDatasetAccessConnection, RDFDatasetConnection, SparqlQueryConnection, SparqlUpdateConnection, Transactional

    public class RDFConnectionFuseki
extends RDFConnectionRemote
    Implementation of the RDFConnection interface for connecting to an Apache Jena Fuseki.

    This adds the ability to work with blank nodes across the network.
